  "text": "From Equation (5), it can be concluded that the Q values of drive and sense modes can affect the mechanical sensitivity. According to the simulation results mentioned later, the resonant frequencies of drive and sense modes vary with the Q values. Hence, in order to estimate the performance of DRG more correctly, a new evaluation indicator IQf is mentioned according to [CITATION_1] :",
